BellaDati,is,a,data,analysis,and,management,service,Users,can,connect,their,databases,and,cloud,services,such,as,MySQL,and,Twitter,to,BellaDati,s,business,dashboards,to,produce,analytical,reports,graphs,and,charts,They,can,then,integrate,the,results,and,visualizations,onto,other,platforms,The,API,is,a,RESTful,protocol,with,JSON,responses,that,gives,developers,access,to,their,mobile,product,BellaDati,Piccolo